Character Stats
    5 stats: strength, endurance, charisma, intelligence, dexterity
    Strength: increase damage, protection (dmg, protection)
    endurance: attack turns are longer (attack turn)
    charisma: more loot and stuff from npcs (% of getting higher loot)
    intelligence: magic stuff works better (magicDmg)
    dexterity: higher dodge and attack a little faster (dodge, atkSpeed)
    
Weapons
    Enchantment System
    Gallowglass (sword)
    Kukri (machete)
    Trident (pitchfork)
    Limited capacity ranged (bows w/ arrows, throwing stars, throwing axes, etc.)
    Epéé (small sword)
    Bō (staff)
